  <description>
    <p>Xash3D-FWGS is a fork of the Half-Life compatible Xash3D engine with many new features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>High portability to multiple platforms</li>
      <li>Advanced multiplayer</li>
      <li>Touchscreen and gamepad support</li>
      <li>And much more</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This is a Flatpak distribution of Ryan C. Gordon's Linux port of the game, for
        ease of use as the game can be difficult to run on modern systems.</p>
    <p><em>PLEASE NOTE:</em> This Flatpak does <em>not</em> include the Half-Life game data. You will need
        to supply it, either by installing it in Steam or copying the <code>valve</code> directory from
        an installation fo the game to <code>$HOME/.var/app/su.xash.xash3d-fwgs/data/</code>.</p>
  </description>
